  <name>Particle (formerly Spark) Android Cloud SDK library </name>
  <description>Particle (formerly Spark) Android Cloud SDK library
The Particle Android Cloud SDK enables Android apps to interact with Particle-powered connected products via the Particle Cloud.
Library will allow you to easily manage active user sessions to Particle cloud, query for device info,
read and write data to/from Spark Core/Photon devices and (via exposed variables and functions)
publish and subscribe events to/from the cloud or to/from devices (coming soon).</description>
